# Valgate — Cursor workspace rules

> **Neon PostgreSQL** is the database target. **`convex/` is legacy** — do not use for new work.  
> Full guides: [AGENTS.md](./AGENTS.md) · [CLAUDE.md](./CLAUDE.md) · [.cursor/README.md](./.cursor/README.md)

## Stack

| Concern | Library |
|---|---|
| Styling | Tailwind CSS 4 + shadcn/ui |
| Auth | Clerk (users + orgs) |
| Database | **Neon PostgreSQL** (+ PostGIS for geo) |
| Validation | Zod |
| Forms | React Hook Form + Zod |
| Files | AWS S3 (presigned, server-side) |
| Maps | Mapbox GL |

## Core rules

- Default to **Server Components**; `"use client"` only at leaves.
- Fetch in Server Components — not `useEffect` for initial loads.
- Persist via **Server Actions + Postgres** (`lib/db` / `services/`) — not Convex.
- **Always `await params`** (Promises in Next.js 15).
- Schema direction: `docs/database/prototype/schema.sql`.
- Mock data: `lib/data/*`, `lib/mock-data.ts` until Neon is wired.

## Do not

- Extend or read `convex/` as source of truth.
- Add `useQuery` / `useMutation` / `ConvexProvider`.
- Add `/api/uploads/*` or `/api/presign/*` — use Server Actions + S3.
- Put secrets in `NEXT_PUBLIC_*` or return `err.message` to clients.

## Security

- Zod every mutation; Clerk auth **and** org/resource authorization.
- Select only UI fields for props; rate-limit sensitive actions.

## shadcn

`npx shadcn@latest add {componentName}` — do not hand-roll `components/ui/`.

